AttributeList.Text: ================================================================================ LPulsesGenerator is used everywhere a pulse signal is requiered. This function is able to generate pulse without disturbance due to scan time of CPU. This function is able to generate pulse with a fix frequency. This function is also able to generate pulse with a defined time ON and a different Time OFF. It is also possible to hold the function. It is also possible to use the running value of time ON and time OFF. ================================================================================
